title: Aubergine
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Romanian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A semi-upscale, healthier food restaurant in Bucharest's Old Town. The menu has a number of veg items, and staff is able to answer questions about ingredients. The size of the dishes vary, so ask. The interior has hundreds of doors salvaged from abandoned buildings in the area.
